<p>Whoa. Wait. Really?</p>
<p>Moving past my shock to comment on the actual piece:</p>
<p>This has one trick, plays with it in a bunch of fun and unnerving ways, and puts us on a lurch before it can wear out. The edits are simple and subtle enough to freak me out in that &quot;first showed up to the Foundation, what is this, everything is so creepy&quot; sort of way I washed up in back in 2009.</p>
<p>So, yeah, upvoted and glad to see you around again.</p>

